body_html: When I ran the fizzbuzz example in the programmer's guide on tf 1.7.0 as fizzbuzz(10) it worked; it only failed when run as fizzbuzz(tf.constant(10)). I'm updating the docs to make it work in both cases, thanks for the heads up.

body: When I ran the fizzbuzz example in the programmer's guide on tf 1.7.0 as `fizzbuzz(10)` it worked; it only failed when run as `fizzbuzz(tf.constant(10))`. I'm updating the docs to make it work in both cases, thanks for the heads up.
